<br>
But the moral of the story is killing lite blues and blues (all at base, my pet tore right through them, I just casted Wrath of the Elements) I gained 2.5 blues in the matter of 2 hrs.  Yes I know you get less xp for lite blues, but with Kei i could literally tear through these things for about 45 minutes straight before OOM.<br>
<br>
By the way, I am level 55. <p><img src="http://mcof.hypermart.net/cgi-bin/data/pphotos/Kaosda.jpg" border="0">


