<br>
Same strat as always, Lightt blues and low dk blues yielding good consistent xp.<br>
<br>
You won't see the Reavers, but will fight lots of Bloodtribe shammies and warriors. Beware getting more than one shammie at a time as they will take turns casting on you while melee'ing the pet. They cast malisement, enstill, scourge and a few others. Periodically check your pet's buff list, as if Torgor's Insects lands your pet will be extremely slow to kill the mob.<br>
<br>
I'm at 53 and have been getting a solid 6-7% per hour in this spot with KEI up. <br>
<br>
I'll be looking for a new spot at 54, as I'd guess that right now I'm seeing about 60/40 darkblue to light blue. The Cougars, Sunflowers and Light Crawlers are similar but maybe at more of a 40/60 ratio.<br>
<br>
BTW: This is a safer spot in regards to adds, so you can get away with using the 49 air pet if you aren't 53 yet. 49 air was working more effectively than 51 Earth due to the extra beating the root would cause...... <p>Naladini <BR>
